com.google.enterprise.apis.client
Class GsaClient

java.lang.Object
  com.google.enterprise.apis.client.GsaClient

public class GsaClient
extends java.lang.Object

Simple, thin implementation of the GsaClient interface. This simple implementation assumes that the client uses the most straightforward functions of GoogleService.
